<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-52-0388 </DOCNO><TEXT>This paper described the Belgian approach related to training programs.After a short description of the situation before the TMI-2 accident,the evolution of training programs will be presented with emphasis onthe impact of regulation and requirements set forth by the Belgian regulatorybody. The original solution adopted for the use of full-scope simulatorswill be described. This solution takes into account the design differencesbetween the seven operating nuclear powers plants.</TEXT></DOC>